item.title: Insights-X: Reference
item.description:
On this page you will learn how the data is stored in Benchmark Dataset. Tables Descriptions of each table and their correspondent fields are found below: performance_(daily|weekly|monthly)_(seller|buyer) This table contains the total of ok and nok searches, quotes, bookings and cancellation requests and responses times for the buyer|seller and for TravelgateX. The buyers|sellers that aren’t connected are aggregated in “others” for the seller case and “OTHERS” for the buyers case.
